# Social Media Do’s & Don’ts for College Students
### Do’s
- Maintain a professional and respectful profile
- Think before posting or sharing any content
- Use privacy settings to control who can see your information
- Share useful, positive, and informative content
- Respect others’ opinions and communicate politely
### Don’ts
- Do not share personal information like phone number or address
- Avoid posting offensive, abusive, or inappropriate content
- Do not believe or spread fake news without verificatio
- Avoid engaging in online arguments or trolling
- Do not overshare personal life details publicly
